# Guide for translating into your language

For every language you want to translate into you need a
locales/[language]/LC_MESSAGES/{{{ package.dottedname }}}.po
(e.g. locales/de/LC_MESSAGES/{{{ package.dottedname }}}.po)

For German
```
mkdir -p de/LC_MESSAGES
touch de/LC_MESSAGES/{{{ package.dottedname }}}.po
```

For updating locales
```
update_locale
```
